   <documentation>
      <row>
         <Docu><![CDATA[= Action name =
PCK.AUTOMIC_INFRASTRUCTURE_MANAGER.PUB.ACTION.CREATE_INFRASTRUCTURE_PROVIDER

= General description = 
This action create Infrastructure provider which will save credentials to provider on which you want to create infrastructure.

= Failure Conditions =
* If user gives invalid type of Provider
* If user do not give mandatory authorize field for that provider type.

= Inputs =
- Provider Name*: Provide a name of the provider to be created. E.g. New AWS Infra
- Type*: Provide type of the infrastructure to be created. E.g. AWS
- Credentials*: Provide credentials load in a valid JSON format. E.g. { "access_key":"xxx", "secret_key":"xxx" }
- Requested By: Provide name of the creator. E.g. Automic


= Behavior =
* Action will fail if user give the correct Type of Provider with incorrect Mandatory fields.
* Action will fail, if User do not give the Mandatory fields for authorization in credentials.
* Below are the given type and mandatory fields.
- AWS               access_key,secret_key 
- Google Cloud      credentials
- Azure             client_secret
- Generic           it is normal key value pair.


= Return Value =
(none)


= Outputs =
* Return code is 0 in case of success.
* Return code is non-zero in case of failure.


= Rollback =
(none)


= Logging =
AE logs will be displayed in the AE report.


= Example For AWS Type =
- Provider Name*: New AWS Infra
- Type*: AWS
- Credentials*: { "access_key":"xxx", "secret_key":"xxx" }
- Requested By: Automic

= Example For Azure Type =
- Provider Name*: New Azure Infra
- Type*: Azure
- Credentials*: { "subscription_id":"xxx", "tenant_id":"xxx", "client_id":"xxx", "client_secret":"xxx" }
- Requested By: Automic

= Example For Google Cloud Type =
- Provider Name*: New Google Cloud Infra
- Type*: Google Cloud
- Credentials*: { "credentials":"xxx" }
- Requested By: Automic

= Example For Generic Type =
- Provider Name*: New Generic Infra
- Type*: Generic
- Credentials*: { "key1":"xxx", "key2":"xxx" }
- Requested By: Automic
]]></Docu>
      </row>
   </documentation>
